I am excited about the prospect of no code, but am afraid that even with its extraordinarily low latencies on general purpose thoughtware that it will not be performant enough for certain hype-bubbles within the industry.
Thus I am proposing a streaming framework. It is somewhat protocol agnostic. I would prefer no handshake, no authorization and no acknowledgement but let's face it, enterprises are going to want TLS and OAUTH 2.

I am trying to keep it simple (and readable) for every language, I know there are a lot of file extensions that could have code for this languages and of course, I am just adding the common ones. Feel free to add more languages.
